longBusinessSummary: Sileon AB (publ), a fintech company, provides SaaS platform that supports businesses in Sweden. The company offers API-based buy now pay later SaaS product that supports payment business. It serves banks, card issuers, and fintech companies. The company was formerly known as Paynova AB and changed its name to Sileon AB (publ) in June 2022. Sileon AB (publ) was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
